  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dad \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0dad\u0daf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Heavy rains in south-western part",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, an increase in the rainfall in the south-western part of the island is expected from today (3) afternoon.",
        "Accordingly, a spokesperson of the department said that on today (3), heavy rains of more than 50 mm will occur in some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-Western provinces, Kandy, Nuwara Eliya and Kalutara districts.",
        "The spokesperson mentioned that there will be some rains in Jaffna district, and in Uva province, Batticaloa and Ampara districts, there will be rain or thundershowers at a few places in the evening or at night.",
        "He also said that in the western slopes of the Central Hills, strong winds of about 50 km per hour will occur from time to time.",
        "The Department of Meteorology advises people to take action to avoid accidents as lightning accidents and temporary strong winds are also possible along with thunderstorms."
      ],
